org.hps.record.evio

Enum EventTagConstant

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<EventTagConstant>
      • org.hps.record.evio.EventTagConstant
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<EventTagConstant>

    public enum EventTagConstant
extends Enum<EventTagConstant>
    Encapsulates event tag constants for EVIO events as described at EVIO Event types.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      END
      CODA END event inserted at end of run.
      EPICS

      CODA GO event indicating event stream is starting.
      PAUSE
      CODA PAUSE event indicating the pause button was pressed in the GUI.
      PHYSICS_OLD
      The old physics event tag by HPS convention.
      PRESTART
      CODA PRESTART event when run initializes.
      SYNC
      CODA SYNC event.
